98
00:09:12,033 --> 00:09:13,700
I've always done things alone.

99
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:17,000
Living alone, eating alone.

100
00:09:19,966 --> 00:09:21,500
So, I felt that...

101
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:27,866
