102
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:35,866
I...

103
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:48,800
Well, I apologize for asking like that. If you don't want to share, it's okay not to.

104
00:09:52,133 --> 00:09:53,366
It's alright.

105
00:09:54,166 --> 00:09:57,200
So, earlier, what were you looking for?

106
00:09:58,266 --> 00:10:01,200
Oh, I was looking for a CCTV camera.

107
00:10:01,566 --> 00:10:04,800
CCTV camera?

108
00:10:09,466 --> 00:10:11,933
