109
00:10:12,133 --> 00:10:15,500
They are used to monitor the house, the office, you know, to ensure security and stuff.

110
00:10:15,566 --> 00:10:19,733
and maintain safety measures, and etc.

111
00:10:20,666 --> 00:10:23,666
In my world, there are CCTV cameras too.

112
00:10:26,533 --> 00:10:28,500
Oh! Okay okay.

113
00:10:29,266 --> 00:10:30,433
Why were you looking for it?

114
00:10:30,633 --> 00:10:32,200
Is there someone who installed it?

115
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:38,300
If I were to say...

116
00:10:39,566 --> 00:10:41,100
someone took our story...

117
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,300
