188
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:44,500
It's quite difficult for me to give up.

189
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:47,400
I think I'll keep reading until...

190
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:50,833
it explains all the weird stuff.

191
00:16:52,333 --> 00:16:53,333
Weird stuff?

192
00:16:56,266 --> 00:17:01,533
