215
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,366
It's like you're loving someone,

216
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:29,300
If another person feels hurt,

217
00:18:30,466 --> 00:18:31,666
No matter how far apart you are,

218
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:34,100
You'll hurt the same.

219
00:18:38,833 --> 00:18:41,900
I want to hand you a face towel.

220
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,766
Even though we're in different worlds,

221
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,433
I'll always be by your side.

222
00:18:58,066 --> 00:18:58,866
I see.

223
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:49,666
Merry Chrit...mas

224
00:20:25,666 --> 00:20:26,466
P'AKSORN...

225
00:20:29,166 --> 00:20:30,166
I'm sorry...

226
00:20:30,166 --> 00:20:32,266
Today, there's an event at school.

227
00:20:32,966 --> 00:20:33,966
That's okay.

228
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,400
Please take a rest.

229
00:20:36,833 --> 00:20:39,400
Are we not celebrating Christmas together?

230
00:20:43,733 --> 00:20:45,033
