245
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:31,033
Then, close your eyes.

246
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:33,700
Close your eyes, please.

247
00:21:54,433 --> 00:21:55,233
Now, open your eyes.

248
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:06,600
That's beautiful.

249
00:22:09,166 --> 00:22:10,433
Merry Christmas.

250
00:22:12,633 --> 00:22:15,266
So, how am I going to eat?

251
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:18,366
If we meet again, I will cook this menu for you.

252
00:22:19,566 --> 00:22:21,233
I also have something for you.

253
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,833
Merry Christmas

254
00:22:37,233 --> 00:22:39,333
Is that for me?

255
00:22:39,333 --> 00:22:40,633
Yes, this is for you.

256
00:22:41,433 --> 00:22:42,233
Well...

257
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:46,466
I know your world might have things like this.

258
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:49,266
But I want to be the one to give to you.

259
00:22:51,100 --> 00:22:52,766
You can use it to write...

260
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:56,300
your...

261
00:22:57,900 --> 00:22:58,700
memories.

262
00:23:01,366 --> 00:23:02,166
