00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,966
Like Christmas in my world,

281
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,200
but not in yours.

282
00:24:24,166 --> 00:24:24,966
But...

283
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:27,500
now...

284
00:24:28,466 --> 00:24:30,100
You've made my world

285
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:32,800
include you now.

286
00:24:37,966 --> 00:24:40,566
You and dad seem close.

287
00:24:45,566 --> 00:24:46,366
That's all it was before.

288
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:53,400
Anyway...

289
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:56,866
You've never shared about your family with me.

290
00:24:59,166 --> 00:24:59,966
I don't have one.

291
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:04,066
My parents aren't around anymore.

292
00:25:09,666 --> 00:25:12,666
I'm sorry. I shouldn't talk about this.

293
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,033
It's okay.

294
00:25:19,366 --> 00:25:20,166
Now,

295
00:25:20,833 --> 00:25:22,800
you're like family to me now.

296
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:29,500
Thanks so much...

297
00:25:30,433 --> 00:25:32,033
for coming into my life.

298
00:26:03,133 --> 00:26:03,900
What's up?

299
00:26:03,900 --> 00:26:05,600
