301
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,000
Don't be upset.

302
00:26:11,966 --> 00:26:13,733
I have to go now.

303
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:16,133
So, hurry back today.

304
00:26:16,133 --> 00:26:18,433
