306
00:26:21,233 --> 00:26:22,666
Don't rush to finish it.

307
00:26:24,133 --> 00:26:25,333
I won't promise.

308
00:26:26,633 --> 00:26:27,800
You won't promise?

309
00:26:39,233 --> 00:26:40,033
Gotta go now.

310
00:26:42,233 --> 00:26:43,033
Hurry back.

311
00:26:56,233 --> 00:26:59,233
