317
00:27:18,666 --> 00:27:19,600
Just kidding!

318
00:27:20,866 --> 00:27:23,366
You can go back now; I'll pay the full amount for you.

319
00:27:23,500 --> 00:27:24,433
Is that true?

320
00:27:24,433 --> 00:27:25,333
Sure!

321
00:27:25,733 --> 00:27:27,166
Thanks so much, sir.

322
00:28:19,900 --> 00:28:22,700
