327
00:28:34,166 --> 00:28:36,733
So I can suggest you.

328
00:28:38,700 --> 00:28:39,500
Vinyl records?

329
00:28:43,433 --> 00:28:45,700
Just forget about it.

330
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:48,366
How about helping me choose vinyl records now?

331
00:28:49,966 --> 00:28:51,366
Left or right?

332
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:04,966
That smile! Are you thinking of the person you love, aren't you?

333
00:29:06,666 --> 00:29:07,466
Uh...

334
00:29:08,966 --> 00:29:12,566
Nah, just thinking about my younger brother.

335
00:29:17,566 --> 00:29:19,566
I thought you'd happily run back to your room.

336
00:29:19,833 --> 00:29:20,933
Are you crazy or what?

337
00:29:20,966 --> 00:29:22,466
I've left everything here.

338
00:29:23,166 --> 00:29:26,300
Um, the post you asked about has received some responses.

339
00:29:26,733 --> 00:29:27,600
Really?

340
00:29:27,633 --> 00:29:28,666
Yes, let's check.

341
00:29:30,033 --> 00:29:31,366
