348
00:29:46,033 --> 00:29:47,266
Nakhon Pathom. Thanks!

349
00:29:51,100 --> 00:29:54,066
Why's he so hurrying? What's wrong with him?

350
00:29:55,166 --> 00:29:56,000
Nakhon Pathom?

351
00:30:25,366 --> 00:30:26,166
What's that sound?

352
00:30:31,466 --> 00:30:32,900
Oops, water leakage!

353
00:30:50,966 --> 00:30:54,166
