365
00:32:21,533 --> 00:32:22,700
I'm going to see a writer.

366
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:23,700
Let's go by my car.

367
00:32:23,700 --> 00:32:25,766
Why don't you ask me about what's happening?

368
00:32:25,766 --> 00:32:29,333
